{"title":"Parcours looks forward to cobble season with Ronde wheels meant for 28mm tires","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/03/25/parcours-looks-forward-to-cobble-season-with-ronde-wheels-meant-for-28mm-tires/","date":1616677219000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Parcours Wheels has a mission to bring aerodynamically optimized, high-end wheels to the world at a reasonable price. The company has plenty of wheels to choose from already. Road, gravel, and even some alloy options are all on the menu. Now Parcours has released the Ronde wheels.</p><figure id=\"attachment_253584\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-253584\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/24164032/Ronde-pairjpg.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x335/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" alt=\"Parcours Ronde wheels\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1661\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2400px) 100vw, 2400px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/24164032/Ronde-pairjpg.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x335/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/24164032/Ronde-pairjpg.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 2400w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/24164032/Ronde-pairjpg-297x206.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/24164032/Ronde-pairjpg-800x554.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/24164032/Ronde-pairjpg-120x83.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/24164032/Ronde-pairjpg-768x532.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfm